<HEADLINE> Ecton Park Wins Risen Star Stakes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW ORLEANS (AP) -- Ecton Park edged by Answer Lively, the  
Breeder's Cup and Eclipse Award winner, for a photo finish win in 
Sunday's $125,000 Risen Star Stakes. 
</P>
<P>
	Ecton Park, second choice in the wagering, threaded his way  
through the field of 12 colts and rebounded from jostling along the 
rail and completed the 1 1-16th miles in 1:44.83. 
</P>
<P>
	Trained by Jerry Quinn and ridden by Shane Sellers, Ecton Park  
took home $75,000, the winner's share of the purse, and paid 
$11.80, $5 and $4.80. 
</P>
<P>
	Answer Lively, the 3-5 favorite who broke through the middle of  
the pack to finish second, paid $3 and $2.80, and Kimberlite Pipe 
returned $19.20 to show. 
</P>
