Clinton would win if she runs for the seat being vacated by 
four-term Sen. Daniel Patrick Moynihan, a Democrat. But ``it'll be 
a tough fight. It won't be a win in a walk,'' he said on CBS' 
``Face the Nation.'' 
</P>
